1. install truffle
npm install -g truffle
https://truffleframework.com/docs/truffle/getting-started/installation

2. install ganache (in mem ethereum)
https://truffleframework.com/ganache

3. install metamask, connect metamask to ganache,
import some accounts from ganache.
https://metamask.io/

4. install lite-server
npm install lite-server --save-dev

5. deploy contract
truffle migrate --reset

6. run 
npm run dev

start gateway:
1. set up flask (http://flask.pocoo.org/docs/0.12/installation/#installation)
   cd gateway
   sudo pip install virtualenv
   virtualenv venv
   . venv/bin/activate
   pip install Flask
   pip install -U flask-cors

2. start gateway server
   export FLASK_APP=server.py
   flask run
